title: *PATREON PREVIEW* Throwing Fits Q4 Shareholders AMA Pt. II
description:
The Core Four return to the hot seat, answering your questions in the finale of our latest AMA. Topics include, but are not limited to: brands for every occasion, big things coming, going green, music industry toxicity, engagement rings, incepting your sig other, booking talent, guilty pleasure zoovies, the future of podcasting, brands ahead of their time, grails, finding true love, teaching and mentoring, moving to New York and much more on this Patreon-exclusive boyz only edition of The Only Podcast That Matters™.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
